    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Use find to located it.  It should be under <code>/usr</code> somewhere:</p>\n\n<pre><code>find /usr -name java\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>When running the command, if there are too many \"Permission denied\" message obfuscating the actual found results then, simply redirect stderr to /dev/null</p>\n\n<pre><code>find /usr -name java 2&gt; /dev/null\n</code></pre>\n"
